name: Strength & Power
description: Strength and power exercises to improve physical performance.

workout_groups.name: Superhuman Strength & Power
workout_groups.description: Extreme strength and durability training to push the limits of human potential.

workouts.name: Atlas Lift
workouts.description: Lift a 500+ lb stone or object from the ground onto a platform.

workouts.name: Car Push Sprints
workouts.description: Push a full-sized vehicle in a sprint motion.

workouts.name: Deadlift to Overhead Press
workouts.description: Lift 500+ lbs from the floor to an overhead press position.

workouts.name: Superhuman Punching Power
workouts.description: Strike a reinforced heavy bag at full force, aiming for impact destruction.

workouts.name: Explosive Jump Squats with Weight Vest
workouts.description: Perform squat jumps while wearing a 150+ lb vest.

workouts.name: Superhuman Weighted Pull-Ups
workouts.description: Perform strict pull-ups with a 100+ lb weighted vest or belt.

workouts.name: Triple Bodyweight Deadlifts
workouts.description: Deadlift three times your body weight for extreme power development.

workouts.name: One-Arm Bodyweight Pull-Up
workouts.description: Perform pull-ups using only one arm to develop supreme upper-body power.

workouts.name: Giant Tire Flips
workouts.description: Flip a 600+ lb tire multiple times across a field.

workouts.name: Full-Force Steel Bar Bending
workouts.description: Bend a steel bar using raw upper-body and grip strength.

workouts.name: Keg Carry & Sprint
workouts.description: Sprint carrying a 250+ lb keg over a set distance.

workouts.name: Sledgehammer Strikes
workouts.description: Swing a sledgehammer at a heavy tire with full force.

workouts.name: Log Clean & Press
workouts.description: Lift and press a 250+ lb log overhead using full-body strength.

workouts.name: Vertical Wall Climb with Weight Vest
workouts.description: Climb a wall or rope while wearing an additional 100+ lbs.

workouts.name: Superhuman Grip Strength Hang
workouts.description: Hang from a pull-up bar with one hand for 90+ seconds while weighted.

workouts.name: Explosive Lateral Leaps
workouts.description: Leap laterally across a 6+ foot gap repeatedly for power and agility.

workouts.name: Unstable Surface Weighted Squats
workouts.description: Perform barbell squats on an unstable surface to build extreme balance and strength.

workouts.name: Weighted Explosive Clapping Push-Ups
workouts.description: Perform clapping push-ups while wearing a 50+ lb weighted vest.

workouts.name: Back-to-Back Spartan Carries
workouts.description: Carry a teammate or heavy dummy across the battlefield under extreme fatigue.

workouts.name: Human Resistance Sprint Drags
workouts.description: Sprint while dragging a 200+ lb resistance sled or partner.

workouts.name: Superhuman Forward Shoulder Throws
workouts.description: Lift and throw a 150+ lb sandbag overhead to simulate enemy throws.

workouts.name: Full-Body Weighted Rope Slams
workouts.description: Slam heavy battle ropes with full force to develop power and endurance.

workouts.name: High-Speed Resistance Band Sprint
workouts.description: Sprint against high-resistance bands for explosive power.
